commit.message: Used and created drone class from djitellopy_class.py and ML

Fetches database data and makes it available in a matrix
- Last 100 measured points for temp, pressure, humidity, loaded into
3x100 matrix, made available as graph
Used and created drone class from djitellodrone lib
Uploaded new sample from djitellopy while fixed bug from sample of tellopy
Sample code for video feed with keyboard control
Allows local image recognition and classification

Added video feed and basic video processing
- uses pyav and numpy to format the video frames into chunks of data,
which can be drawn on
- Draws each frame to the screen with opencv

Add files via upload

Working version, drone goes forward when clenches
